# Box-Games UX Improvements Walkthrough

## UI & UX Polish ("Top 1%" Quality) ✓
Implemented a premium **"Cyberpunk Glass"** design system.

### 1. Visual Theme
- **Background**: Deep charcoal with subtle radial gradients (no more plain black).
- **Glassmorphism**: Cards and modals use backdrop-filter blur and semi-transparent backgrounds.
- **Typography**: Switched to `Manrope` (headings) and `Inter` (body) for clean, modern readability.
- **Colors**:
  - Primary: Neon Green (`#39ff14`)
  - Surface: Dark Glass (`rgba(20, 20, 20, 0.7)`)
  - Text: High contrast white with muted gray secondary text.

### 2. Component Refactoring
- **App.css**: Complete overhaul using CSS Variables (`--primary`, `--bg-card`, etc.) for consistency.
- **ConfirmDialog.js**: Refactored from inline styles to CSS classes (`.dialog-content`, `.dialog-overlay`).
- **Login.js**: Cleaned up inline styles for links.
- **Inputs**: Added glow effects and floating-style focus states.

